13
00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:27.420
It's all because of your Su family.

14
00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:31.080
If not for your family.

15
00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:32.720
I'm not going this far.

16
00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:33.600
Ly Van Hieu

17
00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:35.480
You ungrateful little animal.

18
00:00:35.480 --> 00:00:36.580
You let go of Yen Nhi.

19
00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:38.560
If you don't lick your face begging

20
00:00:38.560 --> 00:00:40.280
How can I agree to this marriage?

21
00:00:40.280 --> 00:00:42.560
It's all because of this little animal.

22
00:00:42.560 --> 00:00:45.520
