23
00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:48.060
How can we blame the princess?

24
00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:50.780
It's all your own doing.

25
00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:51.880
Can't blame us.

26
00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:53.880
