27
00:00:53.880 --> 00:00:56.520
I'm not wrong. It's all your fault.

28
00:00:56.520 --> 00:00:57.540
That's enough.

29
00:00:58.560 --> 00:01:00.500
What you're doing.

30
00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:03.020
It just makes me feel nauseous.

31
00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:06.460
You're my fault.

